directions:
On top of the hill on your left, parking is limited, ((building B apartment 3))
last building on your left, last door on building, immediate apartment door on your left.
comment:
I am a Trans man and this is my home. Everyone is welcome to use the facility here and I try to keep it stocked with TP, soap, clean towel, shower, and Pms needs <3
I work usually late at night and sleep during the day so feel free to call if you want to come over! (423) 631-2049 
I'm a member of a local Trans support group called TCATS and I hope that I can create a safe space for everyone in need <3
